  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In Finnish Cottage Simulator you can relax and enjoy the simple cottage life; fish or hunt, grill food, go to the sauna, play games, or just get drunk.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The cottage life might not be as simple as you thought, as you have to deal with annoyances that might happen at your cottage! However, you can do quests and favors for other cottagers around the lake, to get rewards that make your cottage experience easier.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Key features</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >6-player multiplayer</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sauna</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1723780/extras/ba89d9466f239ac50ba60f21fffb99c1.poster.avif?t=1757864210\" width=550 height=308 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1723780/extras/ba89d9466f239ac50ba60f21fffb99c1.webm?t=1757864210\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1723780/extras/ba89d9466f239ac50ba60f21fffb99c1.mp4?t=1757864210\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Boat and moped driving</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1723780/extras/9f1eec1dc0218deceb1374bef9453a7f.poster.avif?t=1757864210\" width=550 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1723780/extras/9f1eec1dc0218deceb1374bef9453a7f.webm?t=1757864210\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1723780/extras/9f1eec1dc0218deceb1374bef9453a7f.mp4?t=1757864210\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Beer</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1723780/extras/be709c283826ce8b679b4414ea8a6d73.poster.avif?t=1757864210\" width=550 height=308 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1723780/extras/be709c283826ce8b679b4414ea8a6d73.webm?t=1757864210\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1723780/extras/be709c283826ce8b679b4414ea8a6d73.mp4?t=1757864210\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Neighbors & questing</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1723780/extras/42438c33b3c2dbc353458d6c9740814d.poster.avif?t=1757864210\" width=550 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1723780/extras/42438c33b3c2dbc353458d6c9740814d.webm?t=1757864210\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1723780/extras/42438c33b3c2dbc353458d6c9740814d.mp4?t=1757864210\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fishing & hunting</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1723780/extras/36b42843e6f4facd1499c29c673ddae5.poster.avif?t=1757864210\" width=550 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1723780/extras/36b42843e6f4facd1499c29c673ddae5.webm?t=1757864210\" type=\"video/webm; cod